{"tid":2455502,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"晚上十時半","createTime":"2021-03-21T07:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T07:59:03.000Z","uid":17077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f44db167bea093641346f333ad35b11c5efa2bc7","tid":2455502,"uid":17077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:19:19.000Z","msg":"晚上十時半<br />\n明天又是一個上班日<br />\n沒有絲毫睡意的我獨坐在房間<br />\n或許是寂寞令人思前想後<br />\n是對沒友人或情人作伴而感到孤單？<br />\n還是對香港的近況和未來的未知而產生不安？<br />\n<br />\n房間的昏暗彷彿映射著香港的未來<br />\n更使人徹夜難眠<br />\n<br />\n到底將來的香港會變成怎樣？<br />\n到底將來的自己又會以何種的思維應對？<br />\n<br />\n此時此刻<br />\n<br />\n寂寞的氣味籠罩著房間<br />\n社交網站上朋友的限時動態大部分也是吃喝玩樂<br />\n與你身處的空間形成強烈對比<br />\n<br />\n無可奈何的是香港人的善忘及自私<br />\n令人心生去意<br />\n可恨的是 那些時常把抗爭掛在嘴邊的人<br />\n好像已經忘記了香港正經歷著甚麼"},{"pid":"a9387ce78ddfa2228738747693a30d2db27d8a8d","tid":2455502,"uid":17077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c31f85c800ff58028eb042746358e69a77560e9","tid":2455502,"uid":17077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0b504de7ffaffd209acc89f98cfc41d3f83801","tid":2455502,"uid":17077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3311198700266faa0d0ddb89af7b41f866ac2b","tid":2455502,"uid":17077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:53:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8214eab125f4e5b3f9b8b7b7dbee841ed72915","tid":2455502,"uid":17077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c0ad16ddf0faece4dfe8d539cd2e4f0367be6d","tid":2455502,"uid":17077,